@startuml
title ShopSmart Component & System Architecture

node "Client Device" {
    [Web Browser / Mobile App] as Client
}

cloud "Vercel Edge Network" {
    [Next.js Frontend SSR/Static] as FrontendApp
}

node "Cloud Environment (AWS/DigitalOcean)" {
    package "Node.js Server Environment" {
        [Express App Router] as HTTPRouter
        [Middleware Layers \n (Auth, Rate Limit)] as Middleware
        [Module Controllers] as Controllers
        [Business Services] as Services
        [Service Factories \n & DI Container] as DIContainer
        [Prisma Repositories \n (DAOs)] as Repositories
    }
}

database "Managed Database" {
    [PostgreSQL DB] as Postgres
}

cloud "External Services" {
    [Email Provider \n (Nodemailer / SendGrid)] as EmailProvider
}

Client <--> FrontendApp : HTTPS User Interaction
Client <--> HTTPRouter : HTTPS API Calls

FrontendApp <--> HTTPRouter : Initial SSR API Calls

HTTPRouter --> Middleware
Middleware --> Controllers
Controllers --> Services
Services <--> Repositories : Fetches / Mutates Models
DIContainer --> Services : Wires Dependencies
DIContainer --> Controllers : Injects Dependencies
Repositories <--> Postgres : Prisma ORM TCP Connection

Services --> EmailProvider : Dispatch Notifications

@enduml
